
*4.5* so cool

    ;             // Repeat latest f, t, F or T [count] times.
    [ctrl + w .s] // sp the window
    [ctrl + w .v] // vsp the window
    [ctrl + w .c] // close one window

*4.4* so cool
    visualize the lines and then use the cmd:
    !sort
    !sed ''
    you can sort or del what you don't want in the lines choosed;

*4.3* encoding
    set fileencodings=ucs-bom,utf-8,default,latin1,gbk
    nnoremap <silent> <F10> :edit ++enc=gbk<CR>

*4.2* encrypt
  (a) console example
      [root #] vi -x encry.c
  (b) vim internel example
      :X    prompt for Encryption key.
      :X    if you wanna cancel the key, input a <CR> directly.
      :set key=

